    "attributes": {
        "action": "Expand Bounce Back Loan eligibility to businesses established since March 2020",
        "additional_details": "This has given an unfair advantage going forward in the future to businesses which were able to claim. Businesses like mine will not be able to compete with a company that was awarded say \u00a350,000.",
        "background": "The bounce back loan scheme was unfair towards businesses that couldn\u2019t claim an allowance because they weren\u2019t operational before March 2020. The Government needs to allow all businesses to be able to claim an allowance.",
